      "writtenOn": "2020-07-21T16:01:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Chris, how important is this class to CCPR? The shader builder use cases are not important and we could replace with something like std::vector (and make copies of some values returned to callers). I\u0027m wondering if this is something we need to keep at all.",
